# PantheonOS Fractal Structure Diagram v1.0  
### *The Self-Similar Architecture of the Pantheon*

**Status:** Canonical  
**Version:** 1.0  

---

# 1. Overview

PantheonOS is a *self-similar*, *scale-invariant* system.  
Every part reflects the whole, and the whole can be reconstructed from any part.

This ASCII diagram captures the recursive topology.

---

